Alpine winter sports, which includes skiing and snowboarding, are popular sports activities involving skiing down snowy terrain or a snowboard fastened to your feet.
Skiing is a great travel activity with many enthusiasts - sometimes known as "naves," who plan the entire holiday around skiing in a particular area.
